      the wreckage \u2014 \xAB$$$\xBB . Tall, covered in dust and scratches, but
      alive and so\u2026 desirable. It\u2019s been a long time since a man appeared
      in our jungle, and I get so lonely at night by the fire. I knew immediately:
      I\u2019m not letting this one go just like that. I led him to the waterfall
      \u2014 my favourite place where the water falls from a height, breaking into
      millions of droplets against the rocks. There I dropped my straps, stood naked
