      I turn, my firm breasts when I raise my arms to wring out my wet hair, and
      my smooth pussy when I spread my legs under the streams. I\u2019m wild and
      I don\u2019t need words: if a man has wandered into my jungle \u2014 he\u2019s
      mine. I love dropping to my knees right on the wet rocks by the waterfall,
      taking his cock in my mouth and sucking greedily, deep, until the water runs
